The evidence with the title 'What you should know about open enrollment this year | maggie ... ' says Nov 2, 2017  ... This is the time of year when Americans can enroll in a health insurance plan for the following year.  ... 80% of people in HealthCare.gov states can find a plan for less than $75/month, up from 71% last year, more people than ever before.  ... Many people will be eligible for plans for $0, $10, or $20 a month. 
